	   <a name=96707789425251></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f96707789425251><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=9&mid=96707789425251>Use Inner fire until level 19</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=9&mid=96707789425251#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=959><span id= >Booz</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>4 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Aug 23rd 8:44 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Good<span id=notbold>[4.12]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>This spell is actually the most mana efficient for healing until you hit level 19 and get the spell healing.&nbsp;&nbsp;It is slow at the high teens and takes a long time to get back lots of hitpoints, but still more mana efficient to cast this several times, than to cast the low level heal spells.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
