	   <tr><td colspan=2>Actually, it is from a pure mana vs hp healed viewpoint.&nbsp;&nbsp;10 mana for 20 hp a 2:1 ratio is better than light heal at 9 which is still almost 1:1  While it may not cut it if you &gt;really&lt; need the extra healing, one beneficial side effect is that it helps keep abjuration maxed, which can be a pain since most of our buffs are alteration based.<br>Just make sure you explain it to the people you are with and they should not have a problem.  If they do, either find a new group or bust out the Light healing spell.  I used it all the time solo up til 19, even then I still occasionally broke it out just to keep abjuration maxed<br>Gorthin 37 Shaman NPF on Bristlebane<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
