	   <tr><td colspan=2>Believe it or not a shaman can kill a monster that gives exp at the higher levels.&nbsp;&nbsp;Im a 51 ogre shaman and when soloing I prefer to melee kill blue mobs for exp and weapon skill. Once you can make a pet use it.  Buff yourself to the max.  If you can cast any of the quickness spells do so before engaging combat aslo be sure to haste your pet.  <br><br>1st. You must slow the monster this is a must.  Best to use this spell to pull the monster to the area you wish to fight it.<br>2nd. Smash wittle monster to death!<br>3rd. Root step back and heal repeat step 2.<br> <br>note.  I write this with the exp of my shaman that I have played to 51.  Diffences in gear and race my cuase this to be impossable{but I doubt it} for other shamans. <br><br>ME BAHBAK!<br>ME TANK! <br>ME GREENBLOOD!      P.S. Kiting is for druids.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
